Post to Facebook 3 incredible displays of emotion from Rafael Nadal What a match.  //ftw.usatoday.com/2017/01/rafael-nadal-emotional-moment-grigor-dimitrov-australian-open/   3 incredible displays of emotion from Rafael Nadal Nina Mandell , USA TODAY Sports 9:07   25 Shares 
Rafael Nadal of Spain reacts during his Men's Singles semifinal match against Grigor Dimitrov of Bulgaria   Grand Slam tennis tournament   27 January 2017. (Photo: EPA) 
Rafael Nadal's battle against Grigor Dimitrov   was a hard-fought battle, with Nadal coming out on top after five sets. With Dimitrov leading in the fifth set, Nadal came through and was, well, fired up.
